'''Yin Water Rabbit''', also known as '''Kibō''' (癸卯, Mizunotō, Kisui no Usagi, Kisui no U, Kibō), is one of the elements in the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
It is the 40th combination in the Sexagenary cycle, following {{ill|Ren Yin|ja|壬寅|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and preceding {{ill|Jia Chen|ja|甲辰|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. According to {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Gui|ja|癸|1=Mizunoto (癸)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Water (Wu Xing)|ja|水|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branch|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Mao|ja|卯|1=Rabbit (zodiac)|lt=Rabbit (卯)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} corresponds to Yin {{ill|Wood (Wu Xing)|ja|木|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, creating a {{ill|Five Elements#Mutual generation|ja|相生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Water generates Wood) relationship.
== Years of the Yin Water Rabbit == Years in which the remainder when divided by 60 is 43 are considered Yin Water Rabbit years.
{| class="wikitable" |+'''Years of the Yin Water Rabbit''' |- ![[1st millennium]]!![[2nd millennium]]!![[3rd millennium]] |- | * [[43]] * [[103]] * [[163]] * [[223]] * [[283]] * [[343]] * [[403]] * [[463]] * [[523]] * [[583]] * [[643]] * [[703]] * [[763]] * [[823]] * [[883]] * [[943]] | * [[1003]] * [[1063]] * [[1123]] * [[1183]] * [[1243]] * [[1303]] * [[1363]] * [[1423]] * [[1483]] * [[1543]] * [[1603]] * [[1663]] * [[1723]] * [[1783]] * [[1843]] * [[1903]] * [[1963]] | * [[2023]] * [[2083]] * [[2143]] * [[2203]] * [[2263]] * [[2323]] * [[2383]] * [[2443]] * [[2503]] * [[2563]] * [[2623]] * [[2683]] * [[2743]] * [[2803]] * [[2863]] * [[2923]] * [[2983]] |}
== Months of the Yin Water Rabbit == In years where the last digit is 2 or 7 (corresponding to the {{ill|Heavenly Stem|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Ding|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the {{ill|February|ja|2月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of that year is considered a Yin Water Rabbit month. However, this applies to the {{ill|Lunisolar calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and in some cases, the {{ill|Solar terms|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Jingzhe|ja|啓蟄|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to the day before {{ill|Qingming|ja|清明|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) is used.
== Days of the Yin Water Rabbit == === Selection Days === Yin Water Rabbit days are the 11th day of the {{ill|Ten'ichi Tenjō|ja|天一天上|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} cycle.
